text: Hurricane Catarina was a rare hurricane that struck Brazil in 2004 formed in the Southern Atlantic Ocean == Meteorological History == Catarina 2004-03-26 1306Z.jpg|Catarina on 26 March 2004 Catarina 2004-03-25 1329Z.jpg|Catarina on March 25 2004 Catarina made landfall in Brazil as a category 2 hurricane Category:Hurricanes
